Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由小薰提案的「我們的展覽」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們作為毫無特色的普通高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像淡藍色車票一樣  沒有目的地般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飄忽不定的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.95,0:00:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想都沒想過能夠做成這般大事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起在考慮和準備著  積極地加油著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.37,0:00:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是隨著漸漸臨近那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是會有些不安  變得緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳單還剩下這點了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發了很多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海報也只有一點了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貼在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有我們忘記的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有忘記貼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:01:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我們的展覽」  天婦羅是瀨戶內產的康吉鰻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:06.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一天我就在市內轉轉  幫你們宣傳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是為我們著想嗎  還是故意找碴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:14.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個難題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你們要辦展覽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請收下傳單
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:23.30,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,105)\fad(500,500)}「因為又是新的一年」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.11,0:03:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上到11點了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒有過的緊張感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正式開展！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.91,0:03:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一個人過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:45.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是才剛開始嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天天氣又冷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.23,0:03:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管閒事小鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有人來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:04:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  別那麼慌張嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一名哦  慢慢欣賞…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  選照片花了我不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我一起出展嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小町的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想臨時加入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  能展覽的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在香君的旁邊或者下面怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.21,0:04:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話也許可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不介意喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你的企圖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就按這感覺來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得熱鬧起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這裡面拍得好像都是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.32,0:04:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與香君溫馨的畫形成對比  是赤裸裸的暴力照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  說別人的臉是暴力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.87,0:04:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一位客人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.65,0:04:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像滿足了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:23.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是再好不過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一名好像已經被佔了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:35.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽  奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:55.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也發生了好多事情  真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.65,0:05:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:05:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用那個相機拍的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我一直帶在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅畫是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肉球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面的照片是我拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做熏香好像很難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下我來現場製作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.27,0:06:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這畫的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.09,0:06:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肉球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.28,0:06:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面有標題的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒  心裡變得溫暖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾燥的時間差不多是在白熾燈下放一週
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:51.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}理療系  放鬆精神系 清爽系
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好乾燥會長蟲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰  真是盛況空前啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不能來真是遺憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也可以不必勉強的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是薰做的楊樹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熏香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀惠  這個超好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.12,0:07:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這麼厲害啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能選擇裝飾配品真好啊  你們覺得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好評呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  多虧了您的多方協助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為紀惠很努力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我只是借給你廚房而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起晚了  一生的失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是HOBORO店主啊  真是奇遇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇遇？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這之後有櫻田同學的朗讀劇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話就和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  說定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.74,0:07:51.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}櫻田麻音  竹筍的妖精  小筍的危險冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:08:01.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}加油  雖然很想去給你應援  因為沒辦法  就在這裡應援吧  \N麻音的待客之心一定能為大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記鞠躬了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  我能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是竹筍的妖精小筍的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小筍是個容易害羞的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小筍  出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算叫她  他也不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:46.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小筍  美麗的鮮花開放了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聞起來很香的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:56.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好吃的蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小筍  出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小筍出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筍？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大家一起叫她哦  1…2…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小筍～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筍筍～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.35,0:09:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香君  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了大家  小筍出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這之後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小筍遇到了很…很糟糕的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筍…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲知詳情　請待下回分解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有下次？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幅畫是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肉球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塙學姐  圍裙很適合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬌羞了  好可愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那現在開始我就現場製作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  豆餡配品
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的推薦哦  很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  要再來一份了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得有些害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  每一張都是好照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一陣我看了志保美小姐的工作  就這樣想過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志保美小姐的照片是給人觀賞的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的則是給自己看的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我就想選一些能讓人看後綻放笑容的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家想看怎樣的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了什麼樣的照片會綻放笑容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:44.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣想著反而更加迷惘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是選了自己想看的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.14,0:10:54.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以總覺得讓志保美小姐看了好害羞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我覺得澤渡小姐可能還沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你已經得到了很寶貴的東西了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.01,0:11:11.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能為今天來看展覽的人著想而煩惱的澤渡小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經在不知不覺中抓住了非常寶貴的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.95,0:11:19.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貴的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定很快就會注意到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.59,0:11:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤渡小姐一定能拍下撼動心靈的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是第二章  小筍去了鄂霍次克  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.87,0:11:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有裝剩了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家寫了很多問卷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.23,0:12:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  紀惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.06,0:12:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這上面寫照片很好看呢  小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.16,0:12:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤裸裸的表情魄力一百分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是說小町啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.21,0:12:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能有更刺激的熏香  辣椒之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有蛋糕  希望有辣椒配品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼喜歡辣椒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那種事的話  我會被說拿食物來玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡寫竹筍的妖精小筍我全聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻想的故事很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.56,0:12:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是小筍最後被吃掉了很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然啊  那裡我也很猶豫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.88,0:13:00.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是反之結局就很沒勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:01.54,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老姐的  有認真寫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.97,0:13:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  還有大家  真是很棒的「我們的展覽」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.97,0:13:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們這作為一年結束的最後禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也該準備點什麼作為回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔的預告
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年一開始似乎就會發生什麼的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也寫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明等下直接說給我聽就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:31.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次好好看了小薰喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.23,0:13:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你不怎麼說自己的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你教大家做法的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有作為中心開展了這個展覽的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都使我無比高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來等下要向你媽媽去炫耀一番了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很棒的展覽會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年還要繼續辦哦　我很期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得辦這樣的活動很厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也想辦一個試試看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想看小筍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  奶奶寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.81,0:14:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個很愉快的展覽會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓的照片是你通過照相機的四角小窗  自己所找到的寶物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你給我看了這麼美好的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦展覽真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你新年順利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我跟上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:52.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很不錯的果斷一撞  薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.88,0:15:04.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來做示範了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了香親…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音親  做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要倒計時了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.29,0:15:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:37.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.18,0:15:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.15,0:15:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也還請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝熱甜酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:02.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝好喝的甜酒嗎  很熱呼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:14.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是千尋打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在和大家一起新年參拜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  楓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我也去新年參拜  和小智一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我在發賀年短信的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果斷邀請了她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次楓喵來我這的時候  一定介紹給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎在聽到楓喵要搬家去竹原的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種寂寞的感覺  已經是假的一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千尋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:05.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  我沒哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我也要變得積極起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓喵  今年也多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是請你多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年參拜後我發照片給你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和大家說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說要說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那換她們說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  小薰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了「我們的展覽」的照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵比利他們也出展了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  喵比利大受好評哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  快點換給我啊  薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上5點  群發短信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy new year
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得她好有幹勁的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為從「我們的展覽」那得到了大家的美妙的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照約定我來回禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我可以拒絕嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  不要客氣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火有好好關掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  話說現在要出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拿身心來開玩笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰的簽是凶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾  是大凶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  因為我的是大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼  就只有老姐沒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會超級安全駕駛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山那裡水結冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好駕駛的話  會墜崖的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.01,0:18:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結冰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜崖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止都是不安因素啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  去朝日山看新年日出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真會成為不安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說這路好像錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  導航是騙子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直受您照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再拜託您救援嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  大家小心地下車哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:34.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下車？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.02,0:19:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上好滑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.19,0:19:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山路的話就墜崖了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導航出錯反而是好運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.52,0:19:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰的大凶被我的大吉救了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.15,0:19:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.07,0:20:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我有個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.19,0:20:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然其實是要在看日出的時候拿出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡來著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.43,0:20:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.63,0:20:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了  救援到來之前用這個暖和暖和吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我們是來做什麼的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初日看不成了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是應該去海邊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始變亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像新年要從小鎮那邊悄然接近一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:14.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到小鎮這樣的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在山上  這就是看不到的景色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:20.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山被朝日點亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是從山上看不到的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.92,0:21:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:40.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那座山一定也不知道自己有多麼漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像大家一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.16,0:21:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.46,0:21:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在夢想的途中會迷惘和彷徨  可能會無法注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是實際上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在誰看來都是絢爛奪目的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.54,0:21:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在閃閃發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那座山一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.20,0:22:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰  幫我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.39,0:22:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和往常一樣到來的嶄新的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天大家要踏上自己的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想留住這個寶貴的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓的照片是你通過照相機的四角小窗  自己所找到的寶物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:34.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這句話…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爸爸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這扇窗口裡  爸爸看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.66,0:22:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是爸爸找到的寶物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.83,0:22:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為時光荏苒  會變得無法傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才想留住這些珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份感情現在在我心中沉澱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我和爸爸的心連了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼小啪  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  今後也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.83,0:23:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請你多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.20,0:23:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走錯路真是正確啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人這麼說還真是讓人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓她得意忘形  薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.18,0:23:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許叫我薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  打擾您了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車子滑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.70,0:23:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷的吧  我現在去拿點熱東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.43,0:24:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到電話說  有車子打滑了  女孩們很困擾
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿了這個來  救援來之前你們先取暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.67,0:24:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.56,0:24:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  把這個吃了暖暖身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得寒冷的早晨變得溫暖起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:22.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在眼前的寶物可能隨著時光流逝會漸漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.66,0:24:26.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用爸爸留給我的照片拍下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無論何時都能講述這些寶貴的瞬間的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
